Try putting it in the middle.

560
00:17:02,400 --> 00:17:03,320
Yes. Put it here.

561
00:17:03,740 --> 00:17:05,460
(Xin is so smart)

562
00:17:06,560 --> 00:17:07,000
Three.

563
00:17:07,800 --> 00:17:08,240
Two.

564
00:17:08,830 --> 00:17:09,310
One.

565
00:17:11,060 --> 00:17:11,700
(Nothing happened)

566
00:17:11,720 --> 00:17:12,200
It didn't work.

567
00:17:14,040 --> 00:17:14,880
It actually worked.

568
00:17:18,800 --> 00:17:19,350
Sand table.

569
00:17:19,540 --> 00:17:22,140
(Sand table of Tui, Li,
and Kuang Kingdoms)

570
00:17:22,160 --> 00:17:24,070
First step. Destroy Kuang Kingdom.

571
00:17:24,070 --> 00:17:25,960
Second step. Weaken Tui Kingdom.

572
00:17:25,960 --> 00:17:26,960
Third step.

573
00:17:26,960 --> 00:17:28,310
Weaken Li Kingdom.

574
00:17:28,310 --> 00:17:29,720
What's the last step?

575
00:17:29,720 --> 00:17:30,320
Unify them?

576
00:17:30,340 --> 00:17:31,880
(What does the symbol represent?)

577
00:17:31,880 --> 00:17:33,360
I think the last step could be

578
00:17:33,360 --> 00:17:34,440
Great Kuang Kingdom's

579
00:17:34,440 --> 00:17:35,240
A self-portrait.

580
00:17:35,240 --> 00:17:36,080
national emblem.

581
00:17:36,920 --> 00:17:37,480
Hang on.

582
00:17:37,480 --> 00:17:39,400
Someone wants the world.

583
00:17:39,630 --> 00:17:41,520
He even prepared a royal seal.

584
00:17:41,520 --> 00:17:41,960
That's right.

585
00:17:41,960 --> 00:17:44,000
He wants to unify the three kingdoms

586
00:17:44,000 --> 00:17:45,360
and become the king.

587
00:17:46,120 --> 00:17:47,880
He wants to take office.

588
00:17:47,880 --> 00:17:51,440
Using Tui and Li Kingdoms' power
to destroy Kuang Kingdom.

589
00:17:51,440 --> 00:17:53,040
So we were all his pawns.

590
00:17:53,040 --> 00:17:53,520
Yes.

591
00:17:53,520 --> 00:17:55,640
Using us to sow discord
among the three kingdoms.

592
00:17:55,880 --> 00:17:56,160
Yes.

593
00:17:56,160 --> 00:17:58,000
He benefits from us fighting.

594
00:17:58,000 --> 00:17:58,440
Yes.

595
00:17:59,160 --> 00:18:00,400
Hiding behind the scenes.

596
00:18:00,460 --> 00:18:03,260
(Guess: Chancellor Kuang stirs chaos
in the three kingdoms to become king)

597
00:18:03,600 --> 00:18:05,400
Then why did he only want
to destroy Kuang Kingdom

598
00:18:05,400 --> 00:18:06,880
and weaken the other two?

599
00:18:07,300 --> 00:18:08,880
Because...

600
00:18:08,920 --> 00:18:10,920
Yeah. Why did he only target us?

601
00:18:11,120 --> 00:18:12,480
Because Kuang Kingdom is the weakest.

602
00:18:12,480 --> 00:18:12,800
Because

603
00:18:12,800 --> 00:18:14,100
Kuang Kingdom is the weakest.

604
00:18:15,040 --> 00:18:17,280
(I look down on you)
He's picking on the weak.

605
00:18:17,280 --> 00:18:20,600
He's saving his strength for himself.

606
00:18:20,600 --> 00:18:21,840
(Isn't that right?)
Right, princess of Kuang Kingdom?

607
00:18:23,200 --> 00:18:24,200
How dare you

608
00:18:24,200 --> 00:18:26,360
touch my princess?

609
00:18:26,360 --> 00:18:27,440
One more time,

610
00:18:27,440 --> 00:18:28,360
and I'll marry you.

611
00:18:28,420 --> 00:18:30,100
(Can't mess with her)
I'll stop then.

612
00:18:34,280 --> 00:18:35,480
There's a drawer beneath.

613
00:18:35,480 --> 00:18:35,800
Yes.

614
00:18:35,800 --> 00:18:36,900
(Drawers on both sides under the desk)
Yes.

615
00:18:36,920 --> 00:18:37,880
See if there's anything inside.

616
00:18:37,880 --> 00:18:38,720
It's stuck.

617
00:18:38,980 --> 00:18:40,580
(How do we open it?)

618
00:18:48,680 --> 00:18:50,640
This is black and green.

619
00:18:50,640 --> 00:18:51,680
What's there?

620
00:18:51,680 --> 00:18:52,400
Blue and red.

621
00:18:53,400 --> 00:18:53,880
Hang on.

622
00:18:55,000 --> 00:18:55,920
Color.

623
00:18:59,480 --> 00:19:00,360
The flag bases.

624
00:19:00,680 --> 00:19:01,120
Base.

625
00:19:01,120 --> 00:19:01,890
(The slot colors match the bases)
Pull it out.

626
00:19:01,920 --> 00:19:02,360
Yes.

627
00:19:04,080 --> 00:19:04,920
Green.

628
00:19:06,300 --> 00:19:07,620
(First step. Destroy Kuang Kingdom)

629
00:19:09,320 --> 00:19:09,920
It bounced open.

630
00:19:11,660 --> 00:19:13,300
(Place the flags in)

631
00:19:13,300 --> 00:19:15,380
(to unlock the respective drawers)

632
00:19:18,360 --> 00:19:23,240
(Drawer log: First step. Destroy Kuang Kingdom)
I gave Kuang's defense plan to Tui and Li,

633
00:19:23,240 --> 00:19:26,480
using the two kingdoms
to destroy Kuang Kingdom

634
00:19:26,480 --> 00:19:27,960
and became Chancellor.

635
00:19:28,400 --> 00:19:30,080
(After Kuang fell, he became Chancellor Tui)
27 May.

636
00:19:30,080 --> 00:19:31,320
A spy reports

637
00:19:31,320 --> 00:19:32,840
the princess is dead.

638
00:19:32,840 --> 00:19:33,760
Isn't dead.

639
00:19:33,760 --> 00:19:34,160
Princess...

640
00:19:34,160 --> 00:19:35,080
You keep going back and forth.

641
00:19:35,640 --> 00:19:37,390
(What are you saying?)
The princess isn't dead.

642
00:19:38,000 --> 00:19:39,120
Don't break character.

643
00:19:39,340 --> 00:19:40,520
(Deep into character)

644
00:19:40,520 --> 00:19:41,800
With her alive,

645
00:19:41,800 --> 00:19:45,760
I can't win over Kuang Kingdom's
remaining troops.

646
00:19:45,760 --> 00:19:48,200
She must die.

647
00:19:48,520 --> 00:19:50,840
So that tells us something.

648
00:19:50,840 --> 00:19:53,000
Chancellor Tui,
or rather, Chancellor Kuang,

649
00:19:53,000 --> 00:19:54,320
wants to kill her.

650
00:19:54,320 --> 00:19:56,080
(Chancellor Kuang wants to kill Jin Thrifty)
Yes, he wants her dead.

651
00:19:57,040 --> 00:19:58,140
Forget the investigation.
He deserved it.

652
00:19:58,140 --> 00:19:59,180
(Detective on strike)
Let's go.

653
00:19:59,200 --> 00:20:00,920
(Swears to protect her)
Princess, no one can kill you.

654
00:20:05,280 --> 00:20:07,120
If Chancellor Tui wants to kill her,

655
00:20:07,120 --> 00:20:07,560
he...

656
00:20:07,560 --> 00:20:07,960
You have

657
00:20:07,960 --> 00:20:08,680
Have...

658
00:20:08,680 --> 00:20:09,520
a motive for murder.

659
00:20:09,520 --> 00:20:10,120
(Ke Stubborn's motive)
Right.

660
00:20:10,120 --> 00:20:10,860
(Chancellor Kuang wanted
to kill Jin Thrifty)

661
00:20:10,860 --> 00:20:11,580
(Ke Stubborn killed him
to protect Jin Thrifty)

662
00:20:11,760 --> 00:20:13,000
Alright, next.

663
00:20:13,000 --> 00:20:13,560
Step two.

664
00:20:13,620 --> 00:20:14,680
(Drawer note
Step 2: Weaken Tui Kingdom)

665
00:20:14,680 --> 00:20:16,400
Use my pawn

666
00:20:16,400 --> 00:20:18,920
to frame the Longdong Army

667
00:20:18,920 --> 00:20:20,960
and take out two targets at once.

668
00:20:21,360 --> 00:20:24,200
Pin treason on Prince Tui.

669
00:20:27,480 --> 00:20:28,640
He did it.

670
00:20:28,640 --> 00:20:29,720
(Ke Stubborn was Chancellor Kuang's pawn)
He did it.

671
00:20:29,720 --> 00:20:30,650
(My pawn)
Exactly.

672
00:20:31,040 --> 00:20:31,480
So

673
00:20:31,480 --> 00:20:33,120
my motive is clear, right?

674
00:20:33,120 --> 00:20:33,960
Right.

675
00:20:33,960 --> 00:20:35,640
(Ning Waver's motive)
He framed the Longdong Army.

676
00:20:35,640 --> 00:20:36,480
(He knew Chancellor Kuang was behind it)
And I know

677
00:20:36,500 --> 00:20:38,440
(and sought revenge)
Chancellor Kuang

678
00:20:38,440 --> 00:20:39,280
was the mastermind.

679
00:20:39,280 --> 00:20:39,640
This is the first.

680
00:20:39,640 --> 00:20:40,040
Second,

681
00:20:40,360 --> 00:20:41,680
your motives

682
00:20:41,680 --> 00:20:42,320
are clear too.

683
00:20:42,800 --> 00:20:43,200
Right?

684
00:20:43,200 --> 00:20:44,880
You know he used both of you.

685
00:20:44,880 --> 00:20:46,760
Only if we saw this.

686
00:20:46,760 --> 00:20:47,400
Right.

687
00:20:47,800 --> 00:20:48,520
Especially you.

688
00:20:48,520 --> 00:20:49,520
(He Ha's motive)
Take out two targets at once.

689
00:20:49,520 --> 00:20:50,280
(Chancellor Kuang framed He Ha for treason)
Not three, though.

690
00:20:50,280 --> 00:20:51,040
(So He Ha wanted revenge)

691
00:20:51,040 --> 00:20:53,520
(Drawer note
Step 3: Weaken Li Kingdom)
Work with Li Kingdom's fake Crown Prince

692
00:20:53,520 --> 00:20:56,400
(A busy pawn)
and send my pawn
to kill the real Crown Prince.

693
00:20:59,040 --> 00:21:00,240
So your motive is clear too.

694
00:21:00,240 --> 00:21:00,920
Right.

695
00:21:00,920 --> 00:21:01,400
(Ding Pillar's motive)
Okay.

696
00:21:01,400 --> 00:21:01,860
(Chancellor Kuang sent a pawn
to kill Ding Pillar)

697
00:21:01,860 --> 00:21:02,440
(Ding Pillar wanted revenge)

698
00:21:02,440 --> 00:21:04,040
The last one

699
00:21:04,040 --> 00:21:04,840
is the key.

700
00:21:04,940 --> 00:21:06,360
(Drawer note: Step 4)

701
00:21:06,360 --> 00:21:06,720
Alright.

702
00:21:07,200 --> 00:21:07,920
Look.

703
00:21:07,920 --> 00:21:08,840
Read the key part.

704
00:21:08,840 --> 00:21:09,800
Look how much text there is.

705
00:21:10,600 --> 00:21:11,360
It's so long.

706
00:21:12,000 --> 00:21:12,920
Step four.

707
00:21:13,240 --> 00:21:15,000
Destroy Tui and Li Kingdom.

708
00:21:15,000 --> 00:21:17,000
Build Great Kuang Kingdom.

709
00:21:17,000 --> 00:21:18,200
Unite the realm.

710
00:21:18,200 --> 00:21:20,000
Dominate the world.

711
00:21:20,000 --> 00:21:20,480
Okay.

712
00:21:20,480 --> 00:21:21,040
Dominate.

713
00:21:21,480 --> 00:21:22,240
First,

714
00:21:22,240 --> 00:21:24,640
gather grain and money.

715
00:21:25,040 --> 00:21:27,600
(Chancellor Tui (Kuang), Lord Tui)
I lent the Longdong Spear to Lord Tui.

716
00:21:27,600 --> 00:21:30,000
(Lord Tui, Shi Damen)
He used it to kill Shi Damen.

717
00:21:30,400 --> 00:21:32,240
(Lord Tui, City lord)
Then he became city lord

718
00:21:32,240 --> 00:21:33,960
and strengthened my army.

719
00:21:33,960 --> 00:21:35,000
Second,

720
00:21:35,000 --> 00:21:37,000
seize the Qide Sword.

721
00:21:37,000 --> 00:21:38,880
(Longdong Army, Li Kingdom Army)
I once saw 10,000 Longdong Army

722
00:21:38,880 --> 00:21:41,680
defeat 300,000 Li Kingdom Army.

723
00:21:41,680 --> 00:21:42,560
I investigated.

724
00:21:42,560 --> 00:21:44,400
It was because of a secret formula

725
00:21:44,400 --> 00:21:47,800
hidden inside the spear
and sword by General Dong.

726
00:21:48,600 --> 00:21:50,920
I stole the Longdong Spear in the chaos.

727
00:21:50,920 --> 00:21:53,440
Now I only need the Qide Sword.

728
00:21:53,460 --> 00:21:55,020
(What was General Dong's secret formula?)

729
00:21:55,240 --> 00:21:55,720
Third,

730
00:21:56,320 --> 00:21:58,240
forge a supreme weapon.

731
00:21:58,960 --> 00:22:00,520
I couldn't find the sword.

732
00:22:00,520 --> 00:22:02,800
So I can only analyze

733
00:22:02,800 --> 00:22:05,200
the Longdong Army's leftover residue.

734
00:22:05,400 --> 00:22:08,600
But they knew how
to stop ghost soldiers.

735
00:22:09,480 --> 00:22:10,680
To protect the plan,

736
00:22:10,680 --> 00:22:13,920
I had to find their former troops.

737
00:22:13,920 --> 00:22:17,040
(Investigate)
A few Longdong Army veterans

738
00:22:17,040 --> 00:22:19,160
still live in Tui City.

739
00:22:19,160 --> 00:22:21,000
I actually caught one two days ago.

740
00:22:21,060 --> 00:22:22,140
(Longdong Army veterans
are still in Tui City)

741
00:22:22,760 --> 00:22:24,800
Finally, capture Tui City.

742
00:22:24,800 --> 00:22:26,040
On May 28,

743
00:22:26,520 --> 00:22:28,680
I obtained Ning Waver's Qide Sword.

744
00:22:28,680 --> 00:22:30,440
With the Longdong Spear and Qide Sword,

745
00:22:30,440 --> 00:22:31,360
and my ghost soldiers ready,

746
00:22:31,360 --> 00:22:34,760
I only need to seize Tui City

747
00:22:34,760 --> 00:22:35,120
and frame...

748
00:22:35,680 --> 00:22:36,400
Wait a second.

749
00:22:36,400 --> 00:22:37,760
The ghost soldiers are coming.

750
00:22:38,320 --> 00:22:38,840
Wait.

751
00:22:40,360 --> 00:22:40,920
Don't be afraid.

752
00:22:44,360 --> 00:22:44,680
Princess,

753
00:22:45,800 --> 00:22:46,940
(I'm here)
Don't be afraid.

754
00:22:48,540 --> 00:22:49,220
(A very macho performance)

755
00:22:49,360 --> 00:22:50,320
You're scaring me.

756
00:22:52,320 --> 00:22:53,120
Don't worry, it'll be fine.

757
00:22:55,740 --> 00:22:57,980
(Find a table for cover)

758
00:22:58,360 --> 00:23:00,200
If you stay there,
they'll all attack you.

759
00:23:00,880 --> 00:23:01,520
Don't stay there.

760
00:23:01,520 --> 00:23:02,800
Stay with Jin.

761
00:23:03,320 --> 00:23:03,960
Come here.

762
00:23:05,960 --> 00:23:07,600
I think the ghost soldiers will rush in.

763
00:23:09,520 --> 00:23:10,360
Wait, Ning.

764
00:23:10,880 --> 00:23:11,120
Ning.

765
00:23:11,120 --> 00:23:12,120
What...

766
00:23:12,120 --> 00:23:13,390
(Not quite okay)
What date was it?

767
00:23:13,400 --> 00:23:15,360
May 28.

768
00:23:15,360 --> 00:23:16,160
My sword went missing.

769
00:23:17,720 --> 00:23:20,840
I only need to use the ghost soldiers
to seize Tui City,

770
00:23:20,840 --> 00:23:22,560
frame Li Kingdom,

771
00:23:22,560 --> 00:23:24,840
start a war,

772
00:23:24,840 --> 00:23:26,760
and benefit from the chaos.

773
00:23:27,480 --> 00:23:28,960
My spies recently reported.

774
00:23:28,960 --> 00:23:30,000
In Tui City,

775
00:23:30,000 --> 00:23:31,160
there are Ning Waver,

776
00:23:31,160 --> 00:23:32,480
Ke Stubborn,

777
00:23:32,480 --> 00:23:33,800
Ding Pillar,

778
00:23:33,800 --> 00:23:35,240
He Ha,

779
00:23:35,240 --> 00:23:37,680
Jin Thrifty, and Yang Glory.

780
00:23:37,680 --> 00:23:39,560
The six are no ordinary people.

781
00:23:41,520 --> 00:23:42,880
To be safe...

782
00:23:45,420 --> 00:23:46,340
(Feeling uneasy)

783
00:23:46,360 --> 00:23:49,920
... set up a trap banquet first.

784
00:23:50,360 --> 00:23:52,040
Once they are eliminated,

785
00:23:52,560 --> 00:23:54,720
Tui City will be within reach.

786
00:23:54,720 --> 00:23:56,840
I knew something was off with the pineapple.

787
00:23:57,480 --> 00:23:58,840
When we all toasted together.

788
00:23:58,840 --> 00:24:00,280
Cheers.

789
00:24:00,280 --> 00:24:01,280
Come on.

790
00:24:01,280 --> 00:24:01,480
Here.

791
00:24:01,480 --> 00:24:02,040
Cheers.

792
00:24:05,180 --> 00:24:06,260
(A huge bite)

793
00:24:07,320 --> 00:24:08,320
We all ate it.

794
00:24:08,320 --> 00:24:10,760
No wonder I feel drained.

795
00:24:11,360 --> 00:24:12,480
But you ate the most.

796
00:24:12,480 --> 00:24:14,520
(Questioning)
Jin gave you a ton.

797
00:24:14,520 --> 00:24:15,400
And you ate all of it.

798
00:24:15,880 --> 00:24:16,480
I...

799
00:24:16,500 --> 00:24:18,500
(Prince Tui is at an age of growth)

800
00:24:21,580 --> 00:24:23,660
(A note left by Craftsman Tui)

801
00:24:23,680 --> 00:24:25,760
One square on the sand table

802
00:24:25,760 --> 00:24:26,560
has been opened.

803
00:24:26,620 --> 00:24:28,940
(One of the four drawers
was opened by the culprit)

804
00:24:29,240 --> 00:24:31,840
Another key clue is missing.

805
00:24:32,600 --> 00:24:34,000
In these drawers,

806
00:24:34,480 --> 00:24:36,120
something was taken

807
00:24:36,120 --> 00:24:38,640
(A key clue is missing)
after the culprit arrived.

808
00:24:38,640 --> 00:24:40,040
The evidence is missing.

809
00:24:40,040 --> 00:24:41,560
What was it?

810
00:24:41,580 --> 00:24:43,620
(What did the culprit take?)

811
00:24:43,640 --> 00:24:44,840
I just thought of something.

812
00:24:44,840 --> 00:24:45,480
But I'm not sure if I'm right.

813
00:24:47,200 --> 00:24:47,720
The royal seal.

814
00:24:47,940 --> 00:24:49,080
(Is the royal seal (Prince Li's seal)
the missing evidence?)

815
00:24:49,080 --> 00:24:49,680
Because only you had

816
00:24:49,680 --> 00:24:50,760
a fake royal seal.

817
00:24:50,760 --> 00:24:51,160
Right.

818
00:24:51,160 --> 00:24:51,720
Yes.

819
00:24:51,920 --> 00:24:53,200
I carved one

820
00:24:53,200 --> 00:24:54,360
to remind myself every day

821
00:24:55,120 --> 00:24:57,360
(The fake Prince Li's seal he made)
that this disaster must be destroyed.

822
00:24:58,000 --> 00:24:58,360
Right.

823
00:24:58,960 --> 00:25:01,360
It could also be your seal.

824
00:25:01,360 --> 00:25:02,480
If you took it back,

825
00:25:02,480 --> 00:25:03,640
you could use it against your brother.

826
00:25:04,640 --> 00:25:05,760
Right, you stole my seal.

827
00:25:05,760 --> 00:25:06,400
Who did you give it to?

828
00:25:06,400 --> 00:25:07,800
I gave it to Chancellor Kuang.

829
00:25:10,440 --> 00:25:11,040
You...

830
00:25:11,940 --> 00:25:13,220
(What?)

831
00:25:15,360 --> 00:25:15,960
Your...

832
00:25:16,820 --> 00:25:18,540
(A painful memory returns)

833
00:25:18,560 --> 00:25:20,000
Back then...

834
00:25:20,000 --> 00:25:21,700
You did nothing but evil.

835
00:25:21,880 --> 00:25:23,040
Back then,

836
00:25:23,520 --> 00:25:25,920
I gave the real seal
to Chancellor Kuang.

837
00:25:26,440 --> 00:25:29,560
(Ke gave the real seal to Chancellor Kuang)
So Chancellor Kuang has real seal.

838
