"What happened to me?"

1110
00:34:47,120 --> 00:34:49,760
The killer could've
hidden in the furnace.

1111
00:34:49,760 --> 00:34:52,320
When the Chancellor opened the lid,

1112
00:34:52,320 --> 00:34:54,670
the killer dragged him in
and drowned him.

1113
00:34:55,920 --> 00:34:58,120
So he must've swallowed

1114
00:34:58,120 --> 00:34:59,680
some of the unfinished potion.

1115
00:34:59,920 --> 00:35:00,680
Right. And...

1116
00:35:02,080 --> 00:35:03,000
It wasn't fully brewed.

1117
00:35:03,000 --> 00:35:04,320
Three minutes isn't enough
to boil the water.

1118
00:35:04,320 --> 00:35:04,880
Right.

1119
00:35:05,240 --> 00:35:05,680
Exactly.

1120
00:35:07,320 --> 00:35:09,480
But who could hide in there?

1121
00:35:09,880 --> 00:35:11,680
The Nether Elders must check

1122
00:35:11,680 --> 00:35:13,000
that no one's hiding inside

1123
00:35:13,000 --> 00:35:16,440
and that the furnace
is filled to the brim.

1124
00:35:16,880 --> 00:35:18,680
(How did the killer stay underwater?)
Then seal the lid and lock it.

1125
00:35:18,680 --> 00:35:20,720
I will begin the alchemy at noon sharp.

1126
00:35:20,720 --> 00:35:22,160
Three minutes later,

1127
00:35:22,160 --> 00:35:24,520
open the lid and add the special powder.

1128
00:35:26,220 --> 00:35:29,820
(Who could've done this?)

1129
00:35:29,920 --> 00:35:31,480
Wait.

1130
00:35:32,880 --> 00:35:33,560
What's this?

1131
00:35:34,800 --> 00:35:35,440
Is this...

1132
00:35:35,440 --> 00:35:35,840
Wait.

1133
00:35:35,840 --> 00:35:36,720
Is this a cabinet?

1134
00:35:36,720 --> 00:35:37,320
It opens.

1135
00:35:41,640 --> 00:35:43,800
The Longdong Spear and...

1136
00:35:43,800 --> 00:35:45,120
The Qide Sword.

1137
00:35:45,340 --> 00:35:47,820
(Longdong Spear)

1138
00:35:49,900 --> 00:35:51,660
(Qide Sword)

1139
00:35:52,260 --> 00:35:53,340
(Qide Sword)

1140
00:35:53,760 --> 00:35:55,360
The real Qide Sword. So cool!

1141
00:35:58,600 --> 00:35:59,320
Pretty cool.

1142
00:35:59,420 --> 00:36:01,460
(Longdong Spear, Qide Sword)

1143
00:36:01,460 --> 00:36:02,780
(Jealous)

1144
00:36:07,840 --> 00:36:09,640
Finally found it.

1145
00:36:09,640 --> 00:36:10,360
This Longdong Spear

1146
00:36:10,360 --> 00:36:13,240
clearly wasn't made
for General Longdong.

1147
00:36:13,240 --> 00:36:14,920
It's way too short.

1148
00:36:14,920 --> 00:36:15,520
Way too short.

1149
00:36:15,760 --> 00:36:16,120
Yeah.

1150
00:36:16,980 --> 00:36:18,180
(Too short to look like a general)

1151
00:36:18,520 --> 00:36:19,760
It's half a meter too short.

1152
00:36:20,880 --> 00:36:21,880
It's not that bad.

1153
00:36:22,360 --> 00:36:22,880
It's fine.

1154
00:36:22,880 --> 00:36:23,280
It'll do.

1155
00:36:23,280 --> 00:36:24,360
(Good enough)

1156
00:36:24,360 --> 00:36:26,120
You don't look very
intimidating with that.

1157
00:36:26,720 --> 00:36:28,120
It looks more like your walking stick.

1158
00:36:28,120 --> 00:36:29,120
(-5 Intimidation)
That's not mine.

1159
00:36:29,120 --> 00:36:30,040
It was my dad's.

1160
00:36:30,040 --> 00:36:30,840
Then I guess

1161
00:36:31,040 --> 00:36:33,280
your dad wasn't very tall either.

1162
00:36:34,120 --> 00:36:35,000
Okay.

1163
00:36:35,000 --> 00:36:35,360
Wait.

1164
00:36:37,120 --> 00:36:38,080
According to the investigation,

1165
00:36:38,080 --> 00:36:40,000
a secret formula

1166
00:36:40,000 --> 00:36:43,560
was hidden inside the spear and sword.

1167
00:36:44,240 --> 00:36:45,720
So there's a secret formula

1168
00:36:45,720 --> 00:36:47,480
hidden inside the two weapons.

1169
00:36:47,700 --> 00:36:49,660
(Something is hidden inside
the sword and spear)

1170
00:36:53,560 --> 00:36:55,080
Can this be unscrewed?

1171
00:36:55,080 --> 00:36:55,480
I think so.

1172
00:36:55,480 --> 00:36:55,920
Yeah, it turns.

1173
00:36:55,920 --> 00:36:56,360
Right.

1174
00:36:56,360 --> 00:36:57,500
(The Qide Sword's pommel unscrews)

1175
00:36:59,360 --> 00:37:00,360
One at each end.

1176
00:37:00,360 --> 00:37:01,360
Try these two.

1177
00:37:01,360 --> 00:37:02,560
See if they fit together.

1178
00:37:02,560 --> 00:37:03,440
Take the spearhead off too.

1179
00:37:03,720 --> 00:37:04,640
Careful.

1180
00:37:06,040 --> 00:37:07,760
This...

1181
00:37:07,760 --> 00:37:08,480
Ning, look!

1182
00:37:08,480 --> 00:37:09,420
(The spear has a connector at the end)

1183
00:37:13,760 --> 00:37:14,880
I knew it was missing a piece.

1184
00:37:14,880 --> 00:37:16,080
Right.

1185
00:37:17,260 --> 00:37:18,700
(Qide Sword and Longdong Spear combine)

1186
00:37:20,120 --> 00:37:21,040
Not too short now, huh?

1187
00:37:21,040 --> 00:37:22,720
That makes sense.

1188
00:37:23,080 --> 00:37:25,040
(Qide Sword + Longdong Spear)
Qide Long... Qidong Spear!

1189
00:37:26,360 --> 00:37:28,520
The Qide Longdong Spear!

1190
00:37:31,120 --> 00:37:32,560
Now that's more like it.

1191
00:37:32,560 --> 00:37:33,960
Mystery solved.

1192
00:37:33,960 --> 00:37:34,880
His dad wasn't short.

1193
00:37:36,320 --> 00:37:37,920
Looks like he was right.

1194
00:37:37,920 --> 00:37:38,760
It really was missing a piece.

1195
00:37:39,280 --> 00:37:40,600
But now it's a little too long.

1196
00:37:41,100 --> 00:37:42,080
(Suddenly too much to handle)

1197
00:37:42,080 --> 00:37:43,920
Now that's a weapon fit for a general.

1198
00:37:44,280 --> 00:37:44,880
Exactly.

1199
00:37:44,880 --> 00:37:45,440
Yeah.

1200
00:37:45,440 --> 00:37:46,360
(Now that's a general!)

1201
00:37:46,360 --> 00:37:47,840
That's seriously cool.

1202
00:37:50,520 --> 00:37:52,280
Wait, let me see if this fits.

1203
00:37:53,520 --> 00:37:55,680
If we join these two...

1204
00:37:55,920 --> 00:37:56,440
Will it work?

1205
00:37:57,200 --> 00:37:58,080
That should fit perfectly.

1206
00:37:59,840 --> 00:38:02,240
Put the box inside.

1207
00:38:02,840 --> 00:38:03,960
Perfect fit.

1208
00:38:04,360 --> 00:38:05,160
Perfect.

1209
00:38:07,180 --> 00:38:09,060
(A secret inside the sword case)

1210
00:38:09,480 --> 00:38:10,120
Wait.

1211
00:38:14,200 --> 00:38:15,760
There's a secret letter.

1212
00:38:20,840 --> 00:38:22,400
We actually

1213
00:38:22,400 --> 00:38:26,760
unlocked the Qide-Longdong secret!

1214
00:38:26,860 --> 00:38:29,100
(Qide and Longdong unite
to command the realm)

1215
00:38:29,120 --> 00:38:30,440
The secret!

1216
00:38:30,440 --> 00:38:32,820
(The secret to commanding the realm)

1217
00:38:33,480 --> 00:38:36,120
Today, 300,000 Li troops

1218
00:38:36,600 --> 00:38:38,280
have surrounded us outside Tui City.

1219
00:38:38,280 --> 00:38:41,320
I have only 10,000 Longdong soldiers.

1220
00:38:41,720 --> 00:38:43,000
(A letter left by General Dong)
I know we could retreat.

1221
00:38:43,440 --> 00:38:44,640
But the people are innocent.

1222
00:38:45,200 --> 00:38:47,760
If we don't fight, they'll suffer.

1223
00:38:47,760 --> 00:38:49,800
We've been backed into a corner.

1224
00:38:49,800 --> 00:38:51,840
There's only one option left.

1225
00:38:51,840 --> 00:38:53,320
While traveling with Damen,

1226
00:38:53,320 --> 00:38:54,160
I found a secret formula.

1227
00:38:54,680 --> 00:38:56,080
Drink it before death,

1228
00:38:56,080 --> 00:38:58,160
and you'll return for ten days.

1229
00:38:58,600 --> 00:38:59,480
Once revived,

1230
00:38:59,480 --> 00:39:02,280
all wounds will disappear,

1231
00:39:02,960 --> 00:39:06,440
(A way to return from the dead)
along with the memory of your death.

1232
00:39:06,880 --> 00:39:07,360
Memory?

1233
00:39:07,920 --> 00:39:10,440
(After revival: No memory of death)
You'll become immune to poison,

1234
00:39:10,440 --> 00:39:11,480
(Immune to poison)
with incredible strength,

1235
00:39:11,480 --> 00:39:13,600
(Super strength)
and wounds will heal rapidly.

1236
00:39:13,600 --> 00:39:16,080
(Rapid healing)
We named it

1237
00:39:16,080 --> 00:39:18,880
the Qide Longdong potion.

1238
00:39:19,020 --> 00:39:22,820
(To revive: Drink
Qide Longdong potion first)

1239
00:39:23,400 --> 00:39:25,800
But we worried that
this dangerous formula

1240
00:39:25,800 --> 00:39:27,440
would bring disaster to the world,

1241
00:39:27,440 --> 00:39:30,040
(Revival comes at a terrible cost)
so we kept it secret.

1242
00:39:30,560 --> 00:39:32,800
But now, it's our only way out.

1243
00:39:34,120 --> 00:39:35,040
I never expected

1244
00:39:35,040 --> 00:39:38,480
every Longdong soldier
to drink it willingly.

1245
00:39:38,480 --> 00:39:39,720
(Longdong army fights for the people)
None feared battle.

1246
00:39:39,720 --> 00:39:40,880
(They willingly drank the potion)
Not one feared death.

1247
00:39:40,880 --> 00:39:42,520
Whoever invades Tui

1248
00:39:42,520 --> 00:39:44,160
will pay the price!

1249
00:39:44,720 --> 00:39:45,880
(Longdong army fights for the people)
From this day on,

1250
00:39:45,880 --> 00:39:49,120
(They willingly drank the elixir)
we shall rise as an undead army.

1251
00:39:49,120 --> 00:39:51,080
(Even if they must become undead)
Brothers in arms,

1252
00:39:51,080 --> 00:39:52,840
(They'll fight to the very end)
we'll fight for ten days,

1253
00:39:52,840 --> 00:39:53,840
and defend our homeland together.

1254
00:39:53,840 --> 00:39:54,920
To preserve our future,

1255
00:39:55,800 --> 00:39:59,320
I kept the truth from
all recruits under twenty

1256
00:39:59,320 --> 00:40:00,780
(Young soldiers hide in Tui City)
and ordered Damen

1257
00:40:00,780 --> 00:40:02,240
(To fight another day)
to take them to Tui City.

1258
00:40:02,240 --> 00:40:06,120
Now, I'm leaving Ning
and the young soldiers

1259
00:40:06,120 --> 00:40:07,480
in your care.

1260
00:40:07,480 --> 00:40:09,080
I know you'll call me heartless again.

1261
00:40:09,560 --> 00:40:11,920
But you're the only person I trust.

1262
00:40:11,920 --> 00:40:14,520
I've devoted this life to the people.

1263
00:40:14,520 --> 00:40:16,880
I have nothing left
for family or friends.

1264
00:40:20,120 --> 00:40:20,880
Maybe in the next life.

1265
00:40:20,880 --> 00:40:23,320
I'll take you drinking
among the ruins again,

1266
00:40:23,320 --> 00:40:25,760
and we'll play chess in the wilderness.

1267
00:40:26,320 --> 00:40:27,520
For now, I go first.

1268
00:40:28,200 --> 00:40:30,840
If this letter is ever found,

1269
00:40:30,840 --> 00:40:32,840
please tell me

1270
00:40:32,840 --> 00:40:34,920
what year is it now?

1271
00:40:34,920 --> 00:40:36,920
Is the world at peace?

1272
00:40:36,920 --> 00:40:39,560
Are the people safe?

1273
00:40:39,560 --> 00:40:41,840
Wherever we Longdong soldiers may be,

1274
00:40:42,480 --> 00:40:45,040
we'll hear your answer.

1275
00:40:45,380 --> 00:40:47,940
(The Longdong army
sacrificed themselves)

1276
00:40:51,080 --> 00:40:53,520
Ning Waver must've drunk it.

1277
00:40:53,540 --> 00:40:55,900
(Ning Waver drank
the Qide Longdong potion)

1278
00:40:56,960 --> 00:40:59,200
He has all the symptoms.

1279
00:40:59,200 --> 00:40:59,960
It might be

1280
00:40:59,960 --> 00:41:01,640
someone made you drink it.

1281
00:41:01,960 --> 00:41:02,880
Wait.

1282
00:41:04,720 --> 00:41:08,000
We only found out
about this today, right?

1283
00:41:08,000 --> 00:41:08,680
Yes.

1284
00:41:08,680 --> 00:41:10,680
No one ever had both

1285
00:41:10,680 --> 00:41:12,440
the Longdong Spear and Qide Sword.

1286
00:41:12,440 --> 00:41:14,480
(The weapons revealed the truth)
This secret is five years old.

1287
00:41:16,220 --> 00:41:19,860
(Why does Ning Waver show its effects?)

1288
00:41:20,560 --> 00:41:23,280
Chancellor Tui gave me some residue

1289
00:41:23,280 --> 00:41:25,200
and asked me to
have a doctor examine it.

1290
00:41:25,200 --> 00:41:26,240
The doctor said

1291
00:41:26,240 --> 00:41:29,880
it could make rotten meat seem fresh.

1292
00:41:30,560 --> 00:41:32,560
You mean the stuff that made

1293
00:41:32,560 --> 00:41:34,520
those kids' skin rot?

1294
00:41:37,680 --> 00:41:38,120
Exactly.

1295
00:41:38,640 --> 00:41:39,400
I get it now.

1296
00:41:40,080 --> 00:41:42,160
When Lord of Tui City

1297
00:41:42,160 --> 00:41:44,040
poisoned those children,

1298
00:41:44,040 --> 00:41:46,480
he used this same potion,

1299
00:41:46,960 --> 00:41:49,320
the one that makes
rotten meat seem fresh.

1300
00:41:49,320 --> 00:41:52,600
So when I tested it

1301
00:41:52,600 --> 00:41:54,080
to help those children,

1302
00:41:54,080 --> 00:41:55,160
(While testing it for the children)
I accidentally

1303
00:41:55,160 --> 00:41:57,640
(Drank the Qide Longdong potion)
gained the power

1304
00:41:57,640 --> 00:42:01,240
to come back from the dead.

1305
00:42:01,240 --> 00:42:01,720
Right.

1306
00:42:01,720 --> 00:42:03,640
Don't let that Longdong rebel get away!

1307
00:42:06,600 --> 00:42:07,600
Get him!

1308
00:42:07,600 --> 00:42:07,960
He got away!

1309
00:42:07,960 --> 00:42:08,680
What did he say?

1310
00:42:08,680 --> 00:42:09,520
A rebel got away.

1311
00:42:09,840 --> 00:42:10,480
What?

1312
00:42:10,480 --> 00:42:11,880
Don't let the Longdong rebel escape!

1313
00:42:14,440 --> 00:42:16,000
My Longdong.

1314
00:42:16,000 --> 00:42:16,940
(Messing with my old crew?)

1315
00:42:17,100 --> 00:42:18,500
(Gear up, boys!)

1316
00:42:19,560 --> 00:42:20,200
After them!

1317
00:42:20,480 --> 00:42:22,320
Don't let that Longdong rebel get away!

1318
00:42:23,160 --> 00:42:23,840
What?

1319
00:42:38,220 --> 00:42:39,420
(Who's there?)

1320
00:42:39,440 --> 00:42:40,400
Quick!

1321
00:42:41,440 --> 00:42:42,720
He's one of us.

1322
00:42:42,720 --> 00:42:43,640
Get inside!

1323
00:42:47,320 --> 00:42:47,880
What happened?

1324
00:42:51,000 --> 00:42:52,280
A huge army

1325
00:42:52,280 --> 00:42:53,920
of undead soldiers is coming.

1326
00:42:58,480 --> 00:43:00,040
(Memorial)
Tui City is about to fall.

1327
00:43:00,760 --> 00:43:02,520
Only the Longdong army can stop them.

1328
00:43:03,000 --> 00:43:04,800
They're our only hope.

1329
00:43:05,920 --> 00:43:09,400
But isn't the Longdong army almost gone?

1330
00:43:10,880 --> 00:43:14,080
They know how to defeat the undead.

1331
00:43:14,080 --> 00:43:17,320
We need to find the veterans.

1332
00:43:17,380 --> 00:43:19,300
(How can they find
the Longdong veterans?)

1333
00:43:19,320 --> 00:43:21,160
I used to serve in the Longdong army.

1334
00:43:25,560 --> 00:43:29,010
(Cui Geng, former Longdong soldier)
Chancellor Tui has been hunting us

1335
00:43:29,040 --> 00:43:29,920
because we know

1336
00:43:29,920 --> 00:43:31,160
how to defeat the undead.

1337
00:43:31,460 --> 00:43:34,340
(The Longdong army can defeat the undead)

1338
00:43:34,480 --> 00:43:35,600
But only the officers

1339
00:43:35,600 --> 00:43:37,040
hiding among the people

1340
00:43:37,040 --> 00:43:38,200
know how.

1341
00:43:38,480 --> 00:43:39,240
The officers?

1342
00:43:39,240 --> 00:43:40,280
(Longdong officers are
hiding among the people)

1343
00:43:40,280 --> 00:43:41,880
The regular soldiers don't know.

1344
00:43:42,840 --> 00:43:44,560
To summon them,

1345
00:43:44,560 --> 00:43:46,360
the Young Commander must

1346
00:43:46,360 --> 00:43:48,520
shout at the tree,
"Your commander is here!"

1347
00:43:49,280 --> 00:43:50,880
Then you'll receive the Longdong banner.

1348
00:43:51,680 --> 00:43:52,840
Raise our banner,

1349
00:43:53,000 --> 00:43:54,160
and sound the call,

1350
00:43:54,720 --> 00:43:56,040
"Defend our homeland!

1351
00:43:56,040 --> 00:43:57,340
Longdong still stands!"

1352
00:43:57,340 --> 00:43:58,200
(Defend our homeland!
Longdong still stands!)

1353
00:43:58,200 --> 00:43:59,200
Someone will answer the call.

1354
00:44:01,440 --> 00:44:02,640
That's so cool!

1355
00:44:04,920 --> 00:44:05,520
Wait.

1356
00:44:06,240 --> 00:44:07,360
Say that again.

1357
00:44:07,780 --> 00:44:09,420
(Potion side effect: Bad memory)

1358
00:44:09,640 --> 00:44:10,880
From where?

1359
00:44:10,880 --> 00:44:12,200
From the beginning.

1360
00:44:12,200 --> 00:44:14,760
(Didn't remember a thing)
After the part about standing.

1361
00:44:16,700 --> 00:44:19,220
(We'd rewind, but he's
the Young Commander)

1362
00:44:19,230 --> 00:44:21,100
(Tui City is still waiting)

1363
00:44:21,560 --> 00:44:23,320
(He's talked himself into helping)
The Young Commander must

1364
00:44:23,320 --> 00:44:24,640
shout at the tree...

1365
00:44:24,640 --> 00:44:25,700
(Focuses on the details)
Which tree?

1366
00:44:26,360 --> 00:44:27,240
I'll take you there.

1367
00:44:27,280 --> 00:44:27,880
Okay.

1368
00:44:28,380 --> 00:44:29,420
(Top-tier service)

1369
00:44:29,560 --> 00:44:30,760
(One more time)
Shout at the tree,

1370
00:44:31,240 --> 00:44:32,880
"Young Commander is here!"

1371
00:44:32,880 --> 00:44:34,720
Then you'll receive the Longdong banner.

1372
00:44:34,720 --> 00:44:35,760
(How to summon the Longdong veterans)

1373
00:44:35,760 --> 00:44:37,120
(Young Commander calls to the tree:)
Raise our banner!

1374
00:44:37,120 --> 00:44:38,440
("Young Commander is here!" for banner)
Rally our men!

1375
00:44:38,640 --> 00:44:38,940
Defend

1376
00:44:38,940 --> 00:44:40,610
our homeland!

1377
00:44:40,610 --> 00:44:42,670
Longdong

1378
00:44:42,670 --> 00:44:43,880
still stands!

1379
