01:11:15,840 --> 01:11:16,440
Who voted for me?

2192
01:11:16,440 --> 01:11:17,000
I did.

2193
01:11:17,760 --> 01:11:18,520
I voted for you too.

2194
01:11:19,160 --> 01:11:19,800
You know,

2195
01:11:19,800 --> 01:11:23,080
he's our team's contingency plan.

2196
01:11:23,080 --> 01:11:23,560
What?

2197
01:11:24,560 --> 01:11:25,760
We're always worried

2198
01:11:25,760 --> 01:11:29,040
that if there's a newcomer,

2199
01:11:29,040 --> 01:11:31,640
they might escape
without receiving a single vote.

2200
01:11:31,640 --> 01:11:33,240
So, for the sake of the team...

2201
01:11:34,160 --> 01:11:35,520
Now, I'll reveal

2202
01:11:35,520 --> 01:11:37,240
the crucial piece of evidence
that everyone overlooked.

2203
01:11:37,760 --> 01:11:38,520
The crucial evidence?

2204
01:11:38,520 --> 01:11:39,920
Do you all remember that seal?

2205
01:11:39,920 --> 01:11:40,160
Yes.

2206
01:11:40,160 --> 01:11:40,640
Of course.

2207
01:11:40,640 --> 01:11:42,800
Wasn't it rather crudely made?

2208
01:11:42,800 --> 01:11:45,480
I found something.

2209
01:11:46,080 --> 01:11:47,280
This is a seal,

2210
01:11:47,280 --> 01:11:49,680
engraved with the words,
Crown Prince's seal

2211
01:11:49,680 --> 01:11:51,120
(Prince Li's seal)
Open it.

2212
01:11:52,200 --> 01:11:53,720
(Prince Li's seal)
Inside, there's the genuine seal.

2213
01:11:54,160 --> 01:11:55,080
There's also the possibility

2214
01:11:55,080 --> 01:11:56,600
that it was your Crown Prince's seal.

2215
01:11:56,600 --> 01:11:57,680
Once you take the seal back,

2216
01:11:57,680 --> 01:11:58,960
you'll be able to deal with Dian.

2217
01:11:58,980 --> 01:12:01,620
(Ding Pillar had stolen
the genuine seal from Qianji Pavilion)

2218
01:12:04,200 --> 01:12:05,600
Who would even dare to do that?

2219
01:12:05,600 --> 01:12:07,160
But what I'm more curious

2220
01:12:07,160 --> 01:12:09,000
about is when, today,

2221
01:12:09,000 --> 01:12:10,520
you finally lost hope.

2222
01:12:10,520 --> 01:12:11,920
He fought until the very end.

2223
01:12:11,920 --> 01:12:13,080
Honestly, I never lost hope.

2224
01:12:13,080 --> 01:12:13,600
Never.

2225
01:12:13,840 --> 01:12:14,500
(Uncover the story behind the scenes)

2226
01:12:14,500 --> 01:12:16,070
Honestly, you were only
feeling guilty yourself.

2227
01:12:16,070 --> 01:12:16,500
(At every Thursday noon,
Dungeon Archiving)

2228
01:12:16,500 --> 01:12:17,680
You must truly believe
you're not the killer.

2229
01:12:17,680 --> 01:12:18,240
Tell yourself,

2230
01:12:18,720 --> 01:12:19,680
the culprit is only acting.

2231
01:12:19,680 --> 01:12:20,560
(Would you stop talking?)
You're even giving other people advice.

2232
01:12:20,560 --> 01:12:21,760
The moment you came in, you said,

2233
01:12:21,760 --> 01:12:22,360
let me tell you.

2234
01:12:22,360 --> 01:12:23,160
I can explain my choice.

2235
01:12:23,160 --> 01:12:25,200
I can tell everyone exactly
how I reached my conclusion.

2236
01:12:25,200 --> 01:12:26,120
Do you know why I accused him?

2237
01:12:26,120 --> 01:12:27,880
Because you started suspecting her.

2238
01:12:27,880 --> 01:12:29,040
Now I'm beginning to think

2239
01:12:29,040 --> 01:12:31,240
Yang is becoming more suspicious.

2240
01:12:31,240 --> 01:12:32,080
I thought,

2241
01:12:32,080 --> 01:12:33,440
if Jin suspects her, and she's

2242
01:12:33,440 --> 01:12:34,240
the "Guiding Lamp",

2243
01:12:34,240 --> 01:12:35,960
then the killer must be Ding.

2244
01:12:35,960 --> 01:12:37,520
(A process of elimination)
Exactly. That was honestly my reasoning.

2245
01:12:37,520 --> 01:12:39,780
("The Guiding Lamp" illuminated
the path to the truth)

2246
01:12:40,360 --> 01:12:42,000
Alright, everyone.

2247
01:12:42,000 --> 01:12:42,480
What's going on?

2248
01:12:43,680 --> 01:12:44,680
Here's the thing.

2249
01:12:44,680 --> 01:12:46,240
Do you all remember

2250
01:12:46,240 --> 01:12:48,400
what medicine we drank?

2251
01:12:48,400 --> 01:12:50,960
We drank Qide Longdong potion.

2252
01:12:50,960 --> 01:12:51,520
That's right.

2253
01:12:52,200 --> 01:12:53,560
(You've really forgotten, haven't you?)
That very elixir

2254
01:12:53,560 --> 01:12:55,440
has one special effect. What is it?

2255
01:12:55,440 --> 01:12:56,120
What?

2256
01:12:57,520 --> 01:12:58,920
Anyone who drinks it while alive

2257
01:12:58,920 --> 01:13:01,120
will revive for ten days after death.

2258
01:13:01,120 --> 01:13:05,040
It is called the Qide Longdong potion.

2259
01:13:05,040 --> 01:13:07,520
We aren't born on the same
day by choice.

2260
01:13:07,520 --> 01:13:08,080
But we do wish

2261
01:13:08,260 --> 01:13:10,820
to die in the same year, the same
month, and on the same day.

2262
01:13:11,400 --> 01:13:12,240
But you...

2263
01:13:13,240 --> 01:13:15,000
I'm not dying. I'm absolutely not dying.

2264
01:13:15,000 --> 01:13:15,740
(The only person
who never drank the elixir)

2265
01:13:15,880 --> 01:13:16,280
Come on.

2266
01:13:16,280 --> 01:13:17,720
Won't you at least see us off?

2267
01:13:17,720 --> 01:13:18,600
Send us on our way.

2268
01:13:19,160 --> 01:13:19,800
Stay with us.

2269
01:13:20,660 --> 01:13:21,900
(What a heartless man)

2270
01:13:23,720 --> 01:13:25,400
If I can die alongside you,

2271
01:13:25,720 --> 01:13:26,680
I would do so willingly.

2272
01:13:29,040 --> 01:13:30,160
My friends, come.

2273
01:13:30,600 --> 01:13:32,160
Today, I have prepared a feast.

2274
01:13:32,760 --> 01:13:33,880
I believe

2275
01:13:33,880 --> 01:13:35,520
that after everything
we've been through,

2276
01:13:36,280 --> 01:13:37,760
although each of us has our own grudges

2277
01:13:37,760 --> 01:13:38,880
and our own regrets,

2278
01:13:39,360 --> 01:13:41,360
from this day forward,

2279
01:13:41,360 --> 01:13:42,880
we're born

2280
01:13:42,880 --> 01:13:43,920
in the same year,

2281
01:13:43,920 --> 01:13:44,960
the same month,

2282
01:13:44,960 --> 01:13:45,920
and on the same

2283
01:13:45,920 --> 01:13:46,800
day.

2284
01:13:46,820 --> 01:13:47,940
(That doesn't)

2285
01:13:47,980 --> 01:13:48,900
(sound right...)

2286
01:13:48,940 --> 01:13:50,140
(Something's off)

2287
01:13:51,600 --> 01:13:54,800
We don't ask to be born the same day.

2288
01:13:54,800 --> 01:13:56,000
But we are destined

2289
01:13:56,000 --> 01:13:57,280
to die in the same year, the same month,

2290
01:13:57,280 --> 01:13:57,920
and at the same time.

2291
01:13:57,920 --> 01:13:58,480
At the same time.

2292
01:13:58,480 --> 01:13:59,760
To die.

2293
01:13:59,760 --> 01:14:01,160
Then, before we depart,

2294
01:14:01,160 --> 01:14:03,040
does anyone have one final wish?

2295
01:14:04,400 --> 01:14:05,080
As for me,

2296
01:14:05,080 --> 01:14:06,280
I spent my entire life

2297
01:14:06,280 --> 01:14:08,480
searching for a sword
by marking the boat.

2298
01:14:09,360 --> 01:14:12,400
Yet the boat drifted away,
while the sword stayed.

2299
01:14:12,920 --> 01:14:15,280
If there is another life, I only hope

2300
01:14:15,280 --> 01:14:17,440
to live it freely, without restraint.

2301
01:14:17,440 --> 01:14:18,520
(May my next life be free
and true to my heart. -Ke Stubborn)

2302
01:14:18,520 --> 01:14:19,800
Well said.

2303
01:14:20,640 --> 01:14:21,720
I wish

2304
01:14:21,720 --> 01:14:23,400
to live a little longer.

2305
01:14:23,400 --> 01:14:24,840
I want to obtain the Longdong Spear.

2306
01:14:25,520 --> 01:14:27,000
I want to become a righteous man,

2307
01:14:27,000 --> 01:14:27,900
One who can unite all heroes.

2308
01:14:27,900 --> 01:14:29,400
(To uphold justice
and lead the heroes of the world.)

2309
01:14:29,400 --> 01:14:30,960
(Ding Pillar)
Well said.

2310
01:14:31,040 --> 01:14:32,800
I hope that future generations

2311
01:14:32,800 --> 01:14:34,640
will remember

2312
01:14:35,240 --> 01:14:36,400
the passionate history we created,

2313
01:14:36,880 --> 01:14:37,960
learn from it,

2314
01:14:37,960 --> 01:14:39,120
and ensure that there will never

2315
01:14:40,120 --> 01:14:42,000
be innocent sacrifices

2316
01:14:42,000 --> 01:14:43,360
or the devastation of war.

2317
01:14:43,360 --> 01:14:44,380
(May future generations
never forget our story.)

2318
01:14:44,380 --> 01:14:45,360
(Learn from the past. Spare
innocent. End the wars. -He Ha)

2319
01:14:45,360 --> 01:14:46,680
I believe we are alive today

2320
01:14:46,680 --> 01:14:48,520
because someone else
gave their life in our place.

2321
01:14:49,240 --> 01:14:50,400
In my next life,

2322
01:14:50,400 --> 01:14:52,960
I hope Thousand-Faced
Eagle King will continue

2323
01:14:52,960 --> 01:14:53,800
to exist and help even

2324
01:14:53,800 --> 01:14:55,000
(May its legacy live on
and protect lives.)

2325
01:14:55,000 --> 01:14:55,480
more people.

2326
01:14:55,480 --> 01:14:56,340
(Yang Glory)

2327
01:14:56,560 --> 01:14:58,840
My father's wish

2328
01:14:58,840 --> 01:15:00,760
was that everyone

2329
01:15:00,760 --> 01:15:02,080
could enjoy

2330
01:15:02,080 --> 01:15:04,400
their ordinary life.

2331
01:15:04,400 --> 01:15:06,520
When the storm has passed,

2332
01:15:07,000 --> 01:15:08,040
win or lose,

2333
01:15:08,040 --> 01:15:10,520
hero or fallen king,

2334
01:15:10,520 --> 01:15:11,640
what we cherish most

2335
01:15:11,640 --> 01:15:13,720
are still the moments

2336
01:15:13,720 --> 01:15:15,240
we spend living each second.

2337
01:15:15,240 --> 01:15:16,800
Remember, the peace we have now

2338
01:15:16,800 --> 01:15:17,920
was hard-won

2339
01:15:17,920 --> 01:15:19,680
by all of us.

2340
01:15:19,680 --> 01:15:21,340
May every day bring you

2341
01:15:21,340 --> 01:15:22,680
(May everyone live in peace and joy)
happiness and peace.

2342
01:15:22,680 --> 01:15:23,420
(Jin Thrifty)
Yes.

2343
01:15:23,560 --> 01:15:24,400
As for me,

2344
01:15:25,200 --> 01:15:26,360
I hope...

2345
01:15:27,000 --> 01:15:27,800
for peace across the land,

2346
01:15:28,440 --> 01:15:29,520
peace for all things,

2347
01:15:29,520 --> 01:15:31,360
and that everyone in this world

2348
01:15:31,360 --> 01:15:33,400
(May peace reign across the land)
find their own path

2349
01:15:33,400 --> 01:15:34,440
(His own path of heroism, Ning Waver)
of heroism.

2350
01:15:34,440 --> 01:15:35,480
Good.

2351
01:15:35,480 --> 01:15:36,640
Then let us raise a toast

2352
01:15:36,640 --> 01:15:38,520
to the peace of this moment

2353
01:15:38,520 --> 01:15:39,600
and the tranquility of all things.

2354
01:15:40,120 --> 01:15:41,320
Cheers!
Cheers!

2355
01:15:41,320 --> 01:15:42,400
Come on, everyone. Cheers!

2356
01:15:42,960 --> 01:15:44,600
Drink up.

2357
01:15:44,600 --> 01:15:46,280
See you in the next life.

2358
01:16:01,220 --> 01:16:04,220
(After this journey,
what did you feel and reflect on?)

2359
01:16:04,360 --> 01:16:05,840
After experiencing this case,

2360
01:16:05,840 --> 01:16:07,360
my deepest takeaway is

2361
01:16:07,360 --> 01:16:08,280
that loyalty to our country and people

2362
01:16:08,280 --> 01:16:10,040
lives in every one of our hearts.

2363
01:16:10,360 --> 01:16:12,080
The Longdong Army willingly
drank the secret medicine

2364
01:16:12,080 --> 01:16:14,200
and became ghost soldiers
to protect the people.

2365
01:16:14,640 --> 01:16:16,160
The people, in turn,
helped the Longdong Army

2366
01:16:16,160 --> 01:16:18,040
protect the spark they left behind.

2367
01:16:18,600 --> 01:16:20,600
Everyone did what they could

2368
01:16:20,600 --> 01:16:22,840
to contribute to peace.

2369
01:16:22,840 --> 01:16:23,760
In this story,

2370
01:16:23,760 --> 01:16:25,280
I played the Prince of Tui,

2371
01:16:25,280 --> 01:16:26,840
who always pursued
the peace he believed in.

2372
01:16:27,480 --> 01:16:29,080
But in the end,
he was stripped of his title

2373
01:16:29,080 --> 01:16:30,040
and exiled among the people.

2374
01:16:30,040 --> 01:16:31,720
When he realized
that the scheming at court

2375
01:16:32,120 --> 01:16:34,320
made his dream impossible,

2376
01:16:34,880 --> 01:16:36,320
he decided to start
with the small things around him.

2377
01:16:36,920 --> 01:16:38,160
Using the money he earned,

2378
01:16:38,160 --> 01:16:39,880
he helped the ordinary people
around him,

2379
01:16:40,360 --> 01:16:42,720
drawing closer to his dream
one step at a time.

2380
01:16:42,720 --> 01:16:44,800
I believe this is also a form
of chivalry.

2381
01:16:44,800 --> 01:16:45,920
As long as we hold on to kindness,

2382
01:16:45,920 --> 01:16:46,880
strive to survive,

2383
01:16:46,880 --> 01:16:48,480
and help others as best we can,

2384
01:16:48,480 --> 01:16:50,200
we too can become a glimmer
of light in the darkness.

2385
01:16:50,960 --> 01:16:52,640
(Inspect)
You don't need great abilities.

2386
01:16:52,640 --> 01:16:54,320
Hold on to your kindness,

2387
01:16:54,320 --> 01:16:56,080
and you can warm those around you.

2388
01:16:56,480 --> 01:16:57,600
Better to die with a voice

2389
01:16:57,600 --> 01:16:58,680
than live in silence.

2390
01:16:59,040 --> 01:17:00,280
Everyone in this story

2391
01:17:00,280 --> 01:17:01,800
would rather be misunderstood

2392
01:17:01,800 --> 01:17:03,000
or even lose their lives

2393
01:17:03,000 --> 01:17:06,120
than stay silent
and live on in submission.

2394
01:17:06,440 --> 01:17:08,040
That's the chivalry I believe in.

2395
01:17:08,040 --> 01:17:10,120
Heroes aren't born fearless.

2396
01:17:10,120 --> 01:17:11,840
They choose to be brave.

2397
01:17:14,200 --> 01:17:15,920
Tui City's peace

2398
01:17:15,920 --> 01:17:18,280
was bought with the sacrifices

2399
01:17:18,280 --> 01:17:19,560
of countless Longdong soldiers.

2400
01:17:19,560 --> 01:17:21,040
Just like today,

2401
01:17:21,400 --> 01:17:23,480
much of the good in our lives

2402
01:17:23,480 --> 01:17:24,040
wouldn't be possible

2403
01:17:24,040 --> 01:17:26,320
without the heroes who bear our burdens.

2404
01:17:26,520 --> 01:17:28,320
I think chivalry is quite simple.

2405
01:17:28,320 --> 01:17:29,040
To me,

2406
01:17:29,040 --> 01:17:30,760
chivalry may simply mean

2407
01:17:30,760 --> 01:17:32,880
that whenever we see someone vulnerable,

2408
01:17:33,240 --> 01:17:35,680
we're willing to lend them a hand.

2409
01:17:35,960 --> 01:17:37,080
After this case,

2410
01:17:37,080 --> 01:17:38,520
I realized

2411
01:17:38,520 --> 01:17:40,800
true strength isn't
about defeating others,

2412
01:17:41,160 --> 01:17:43,920
but holding on to the kindness
in your heart.

2413
01:17:44,280 --> 01:17:46,000
No matter how difficult the road ahead,

2414
01:17:46,320 --> 01:17:47,800
someone must always stand up

2415
01:17:48,120 --> 01:17:50,200
and fight for those worth protecting.

2416
01:17:50,480 --> 01:17:52,440
Peace isn't something we're born with.

2417
01:17:52,640 --> 01:17:54,200
Stability comes at a price.

2418
01:17:54,200 --> 01:17:55,600
War has never been far away.

2419
01:17:55,920 --> 01:17:57,480
We're simply fortunate to live

2420
01:17:57,480 --> 01:17:58,920
in a time of peace.

2421
01:17:58,920 --> 01:18:00,800
The peaceful,
ordinary lives we have today,

2422
01:18:00,800 --> 01:18:02,560
free from worry over food and clothing,

2423
01:18:03,040 --> 01:18:04,400
were earned by generations before us

2424
01:18:04,400 --> 01:18:06,200
through perseverance and sacrifice.

2425
01:18:06,640 --> 01:18:08,200
It was their desperate protection

2426
01:18:08,560 --> 01:18:10,520
that gave us the peace we enjoy today.

2427
01:18:10,900 --> 01:18:15,020
(Generations toil,
together guarding peace.)

2428
01:18:15,140 --> 01:18:17,470
(Next Episode Preview)

2429
01:18:17,480 --> 01:18:18,480
Where are we?

2430
01:18:18,480 --> 01:18:19,600
Let us out!

2431
01:18:19,600 --> 01:18:20,680
Who are you?

2432
01:18:20,680 --> 01:18:21,800
Ke Stubborn.

2433
01:18:23,000 --> 01:18:23,840
Who?

2434
01:18:23,840 --> 01:18:25,160
Are you two putting on an act?

2435
01:18:25,160 --> 01:18:26,400
Are they crazy?

2436
01:18:26,400 --> 01:18:27,680
You don't recognize me?

2437
01:18:27,680 --> 01:18:29,480
Do you know what year it is?

2438
01:18:29,480 --> 01:18:31,000
260.

2439
01:18:31,000 --> 01:18:34,440
It's 2026.

2440
01:18:34,440 --> 01:18:35,200
No, that's not right.

2441
01:18:35,200 --> 01:18:36,600
He's Ning Waver.

2442
01:18:36,600 --> 01:18:37,640
Ding Pillar.

2443
01:18:37,640 --> 01:18:38,760
He Ha.

2444
01:18:38,760 --> 01:18:39,600
Jin Thrifty.

2445
01:18:39,600 --> 01:18:41,760
You buried and sent all four of us off!

2446
01:18:41,760 --> 01:18:42,840
Wait a second.

2447
01:18:42,840 --> 01:18:44,280
My name

2448
01:18:44,280 --> 01:18:47,240
is Jin Da, there's no Thrifty.

2449
01:18:47,640 --> 01:18:48,880
I'm Ding Tian.

2450
01:18:48,880 --> 01:18:50,120
I'm Hehe.

2451
01:18:51,320 --> 01:18:52,600
Something's fishy here.

2452
01:18:55,760 --> 01:18:57,760
Do you know what this sound is?

2453
01:18:57,760 --> 01:18:59,040
The sound of the ghost soldier armor.

2454
01:18:59,040 --> 01:19:00,700
(Ancient Prophecy, Modern Echoes.
Same Path, Different Hearts)

2455
01:19:01,160 --> 01:19:01,880
Who is that?

2456
01:19:01,880 --> 01:19:03,240
Isn't that Curator Tui?

2457
01:19:03,240 --> 01:19:04,920
Those who wear the ghost soldier armor

2458
01:19:04,920 --> 01:19:06,640
(The armor causes its wearer to bleed)
will bleed and die.

2459
01:19:06,640 --> 01:19:07,560
He put it on.

2460
